                <div class="client-logo-item"><img src="images/sec3/img5.jpg" alt="팀 협업"></div>
                <div class="client-logo-item"><img src="images/sec3/img6.jpg" alt="전문 분석"></div>
                <div class="client-logo-item"><img src="images/sec3/img1.jpg" alt="교육 프로그램"></div>
